er_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.506551767719637e-19, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team South Africa'smen's rugby sevens team, known as theBlitzbokson the world circuit, head into their first match at theParis Olympics 2024on Wednesday, 24 July as one of the form teams.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section  Despite having to win their way through final qualifying, they arrived in Paris on the back of six straight victories in Monaco last month, beating Mexico, Tonga, Chile, Uganda, Canada and Great Britain along the way.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.1198510243839003e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"score\": 0.7544553400554581, \"rank\": 0.3254593412218398, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\"}, {\"begin\": 844, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999801126918557, \"rank\": 9.721156950466745e-05, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, now the temperature ramps up and it will reach boiling point in the 69 000-capacity Stade de France on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's team will faceIrelandin the first of their three matches inPool A.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also in the tough grouping areNew ZealandandJapan.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the third time sevens rugby has been included in the Olympic programme and Team SA are eager to rise to the occasion, having won bronze at Rio de Janeiro 2016, but missing out on a medal in Tokyo in 2021.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.506551767719637e-19, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8732778254525917, \"rank\": 0.14504648009003968, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The old cliche of one match at a time is exactly what the mindset of coachPhilip Snymanwill be as he prepares his troops for battle.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, Ireland themselves come off the back of a successful world series season and were in fact the last country to beat Team SA, winning 12-7 to take fifth place in Madrid in June.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1528, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.66072546961355e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.506551767719637e-19, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1688, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 0.6589859031151465, \"rank\": 0.5174810385849715, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throw that into the rugby mix of South Africa's rivalry with Ireland and there is anextra edge to the openeragainst Ireland.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.095058293297506e-12, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1766, \"end\": 1773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.66072546961355e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.66072546961355e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosko Specmanwon't object to being called a veteran and the 35-year-old has been there and done that in both formats of the game.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"score\": 0.9999999998990461, \"rank\": 1.0095987045624917e-10, \"text\": \"Rosko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also part of the Team SA squad that claimed gold at Rio 2016, as was Snyman.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.506551767719637e-19, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's very true,\\\" said Specman after a training session in Paris.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}, {\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.1198510243839003e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are out to settle a score.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They beat us the last time we played them in Sevens and then when it came to the 15's they won the second Test to level the series at 1-all.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This time though we are out to make it two-one in our favour.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know that it's always back and forth against Ireland.\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.66072546961355e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have given us a hard time throughout the season and they often punch first.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know what they are going to bring and we will counter that.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is great energy about this group and we have a nice plan in store,\\\" Specman added.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2625, \"end\": 2632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are three groups of four teams in each of the men's and women's competitions.\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The women also have a tough pool to encounter, with opposition looming in the form of Australia, Ireland and Great Britain.\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2811, \"end\": 2820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0576133514216093e-12, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2822, \"end\": 2829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.66072546961355e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9848208265917765, \"rank\": 0.013602438714777499, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Blitzboks will take on Ireland on Wednesday, 24 July at17:30(SA time), followed by their clash against New Zealand at21:30(SA time) that evening.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2877, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.66072546961355e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2957, \"end\